%2Fmilitary-stations%2Frussia%2Fthe-buzzer%22%3Estation%20known%20as%0A%22UVB-76%22%20increased%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20mystery%20of%20this%20station%20inspired%20us%20to%0Aseek%20out%20other%20similarly%20mysterious%20stations%2C%20and%20thus%20into%20the%0Abizarre%20world%20of%20shortwave%20radio's%20infamous%20number%20stations.%0AGreatly%20inspired%20by%20the%20work%20of%20other%20online%20groups%2C%20Priyom%20has%0Abeen%20developed%20to%20easily%20bring%20both%20the%20current%20and%20historical%0Ainformation%20about%20number%20stations%20into%20one%20comprehensive%20site%2C%20and%0Ato%20make%20the%20recording%2C%20listening%20and%20analysis%20of%20shortwave%20radio%2C%0Anumber%20stations%2C%20and%20all%20related%20on-air%20enigmas%20accessible%20to%20all%0Awho%20are%20interested.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMission%20statement%20and%20ideology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EInformation%20wants%20to%20be%20free%2C%20and%20the%20progression%20of%20humanity%20is%0Adetermined%20by%20this%20free%20exchange%20of%20ideas%20and%20information.%20Our%0Amission%20is%20to%20provide%20information%20to%20the%20public%2C%20freely%2C%20without%0Abeing%20tainted%20by%20politics%2C%20ideology%2C%20or%20other%20barriers.%20We%20aim%20to%0Apresent%20the%20ongoing%2C%20clandestine%20world%20to%20you%2C%20without%20distorting%0Athe%20facts%20due%20to%20anyone's%20own%20personal%20beliefs.%20The%20members%20of%20the%0APriyom%20team%20and%20community%20all%20have%20differing%20and%20conflicting%0Apolitical%20views%2C%20and%20our%20aim%20is%20to%20keep%20politics%20off%20the%20site.%20We%0Ahave%20no%20direct%20leadership%20and%20work%20as%20a%20democratic%20group%2C%20with%0Adecisions%20being%20made%20by%20the%20whole%20group%20rather%20than%20any%20leadership%0Astructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContact%20and%20join%20Priyom.org%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EThe%20Priyom.org%20community%20mostly%20revolves%20around%20the%20IRC%20channel%0A%3Cstrong%3E%23priyom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20on%20Libera.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20goals%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20gather%20historical%20information%20on%20number%20stations%20and%20where%0Apossible%20present%20that%20in%20one%20comprehensive%20site%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20respect%20the%20other%20groups%20researching%20number%20stations%20and%20to%0Aencourage%20collaboration%20and%20co-operation%20between%20the%20groups%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20gather%20as%20much%20information%20about%20Number%20stations%20as%0Apossible%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20present%20all%20the%20information%20in%20a%20clear%20and%20concise%20way%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20make%20all%20information%20obtainable%20about%20number%20station%0Atransmissions%20available%20to%20the%20public%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20present%20evidence%20of%20Number%20stations%20by%20recording%20and%0Atranscribing%20Number%20station%20activity%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20make%20public%20listening%20of%20Number%20stations%20more%20accessible%20by%0Apublishing%20schedules%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20understand%20the%20relationships%20between%20stations%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20do%20all%20of%20the%20above%20publically%20and%20in%20the%20open%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20drag%20the%20radio%20listening%20community%20online%20and%20into%20the%2021st%0Acentury%20(kicking%20and%20screaming%20if%20needed)%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20encourage%20standards%20in%20the%20recording%20and%20logging%20of%20stations%0Aallowing%20better%20analysis%20and%20collaboration%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%0A%3Cli%3ETo%20build%20a%20community%20of%20listeners%20around%20the%20globe%20to%20cover%20all%0Afrequencies%20at%20all%20times%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%0A%3C!--%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20people%20involved%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EArgonn%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EAvare%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3ECrysisLTU%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3ECzez%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3Edanix111%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3Edude1